entor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>A New Block Directory To Quickly Find New Blocks</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Perhaps one of the best features of WordPress’s new and improved block editor is that you can quickly search for the blocks you might need for your content with the new block directory feature.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Simply search for any block that you might need, and the block directory will pull up the best matching results for you based on WordPress’s list of</span><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/browse/block/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b> plugins categorized as blocks</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3000d46 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"3000d46\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58080d6 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"58080d6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e23cbb1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e23cbb1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1920\" height=\"935\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"WordPress 5.5 Next Release\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2.png 1920w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-600x292.png 600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-1600x779.png 1600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-768x374.png 768w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-1536x748.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" title=\"WordPress 5.5 New Features: What&#039;s Coming In Next Release 83\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e80bfcf elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"e80bfcf\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4cd26f elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"d4cd26f\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b76d44 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1b76d44\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>Introduction Of New Block Patterns For Designing Cool Layouts</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Another cool feature that’s coming with the release of <strong>WordPress 5.5</strong> is the introduction of new block patterns. These are ready-to-use premade blocks that will help you design the layout of your posts and pages instantly with just a few clicks. The new release comes with several of these new block patterns by default, but the collection will increase as more patterns are registered with updated WordPress themes, plugins and more. </span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-802ef69 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"802ef69\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25c9557 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"25c9557\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-81f4844 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"81f4844\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1920\" height=\"935\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"WordPress 5.5 Next Release\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3.png 1920w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3-600x292.png 600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3-1600x779.png 1600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3-768x374.png 768w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3-1536x748.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" title=\"WordPress 5.5 New Features: What&#039;s Coming In Next Release 84\">					